      *@1 입력파라미터조립
      *   그룹회사코드
           MOVE  IN-GROUP-CO-CD
             TO  RJLR018-GROUP-CO-CD

      *   기업집단그룹코드
           MOVE  IN-CORP-CLCT-GROUP-CD
             TO  RJLR018-CORP-CLCT-GROUP-CD

      *   기업집단등록코드
           MOVE  IN-CORP-CLCT-REGI-CD
             TO  RJLR018-CORP-CLCT-REGI-CD

      *   평가년월일
           MOVE  IN-VALUA-YMD
             TO  RJLR018-VALUA-YMD

      *   기업집단처리단계구분
           MOVE  IN-CORP-CP-STGE-DSTCD
             TO  RJLR018-CORP-CP-STGE-DSTCD

      *   최종집단등급구분
           MOVE  IN-LAST-CLCT-GRD-DSTCD
             TO  RJLR018-LAST-CLCT-GRD-DSTCD

      *@1 기업집단평가기본수보(THKJLR018) INSERT
           #DYDBIO  INSERT-CMD-Y TKJLR018-PK TRJLR018-REC

      *   리턴코드가 정상이 아니면 에러처리
           EVALUATE  TRUE
               WHEN  COND-DBIO-OK
                     ADD   CO-NUM-1    TO  WK-AC-INSERT-CNT
               WHEN  COND-DBIO-DUPM
           #USRLOG '집단그룹코드-803 : ' RJLR018-CORP-CLCT-GROUP-CD
               WHEN  OTHER
           #USRLOG '집단그룹코드-ERR : ' RJLR018-CORP-CLCT-GROUP-CD
                     MOVE 'KJLR018'    TO  XZUGEROR-I-TBL-ID
                     MOVE 'INSERT'     TO  XZUGEROR-I-FUNC-CD
                     MOVE  DBIO-SQLCODE
                                       TO  XZUGEROR-I-SQL-CD
                     MOVE 'INSERT시오류가발생했습니다'
                                       TO  XZUGEROR-I-MSG
                     #ERROR  CO-EBM02001 CO-UBM02001 DBIO-STAT
                     #OKEXIT CO-CHA-08
            END-EVALUATE
           .
       S3220-KJLR018-INSERT-EXT.
           EXIT.

